net.akami.mask.function

Class MathFunction

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.akami.mask.function.MathFunction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AlterationHandler<Expression,Expression>, PostCalculationActionable<Expression>, CompleteCoverOverlay, ExpressionOverlay
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    NumberRequiredFunction, PiValue

    public abstract class MathFunction
extends java.lang.Object
implements AlterationHandler<Expression,Expression>, PostCalculationActionable<Expression>, CompleteCoverOverlay
    Represents a mathematical function matching the following syntax : name(p1, p2, ...). 
    
 The currently available functions are the trigonometry functions exclusively. More functions with multiple
 parameters, such as log or root will be added in the future.
    

    

    Author:
    

    Antoine Tran
